  "files": [
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-1",
      "filename": "intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/perfect-numbers/yunxi/intro-intro-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.21,
      "size": 35280,
      "text": "数字 6 有个神奇的秘密：它的真因数是 1、2、3。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-2",
      "filename": "intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/perfect-numbers/yunxi/intro-intro-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.65,
      "size": 26352,
      "text": "把它们加起来，1 加 2 加 3，正好又等于 6。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "intro",
      "line_id": "intro-3",
      "filename": "intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/perfect-numbers/yunxi/intro-intro-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.98,
      "size": 31680,
      "text": "一个数刚好等于自己各部分之和，古人称它为完美。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-1",
      "filename": "define-def-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/perfect-numbers/yunxi/define-def-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "真因数，就是一个数除自身以外的所有因数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-2",
      "filename": "define-def-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/perfect-numbers/yunxi/define-def-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.87,
      "size": 29952,
      "text": "如果真因数之和恰好等于这个数，它就是完全数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "define",
      "line_id": "def-3",
      "filename": "define-def-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/perfect-numbers/yunxi/define-def-3.mp3",
      "duration": 2.56,
      "size": 40896,
      "text": "6 之后的完全数是 28，接着是 496 和 8128，越来越稀少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "balance",
      "line_id": "bal-1",
      "filename": "balance-bal-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/perfect-numbers/yunxi/balance-bal-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.14,
      "size": 34272,
      "text": "如果真因数之和大于自身，我们叫它盈数，比如 12。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "balance",
      "line_id": "bal-2",
      "filename": "balance-bal-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/perfect-numbers/yunxi/balance-bal-2.mp3",
      "duration": 2.05,
      "size": 32832,
      "text": "如果真因数之和小于自身，就叫亏数，比如 8。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "balance",
      "line_id": "bal-3",
      "filename": "balance-bal-3.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/perfect-numbers/yunxi/balance-bal-3.mp3",
      "duration": 1.85,
      "size": 29664,
      "text": "完全数恰好卡在盈与亏之间，稀有而平衡。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "amicable",
      "line_id": "ami-1",
      "filename": "amicable-ami-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/perfect-numbers/yunxi/amicable-ami-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.74,
      "size": 43776,
      "text": "220 的真因数加起来等于 284，而 284 的真因数又加回 220。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "amicable",
      "line_id": "ami-2",
      "filename": "amicable-ami-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/perfect-numbers/yunxi/amicable-ami-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.99,
      "size": 31824,
      "text": "这对彼此成就的数字，被称为亲和数，象征友谊。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-1",
      "filename": "interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/perfect-numbers/yunxi/interaction-int-1.mp3",
      "duration": 1.63,
      "size": 26064,
      "text": "输入任意一个数字，看看它的真因数怎么分解。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "interaction",
      "line_id": "int-2",
      "filename": "interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/perfect-numbers/yunxi/interaction-int-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.97,
      "size": 31536,
      "text": "再看看它到底是完全数、盈数还是亏数。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-1",
      "filename": "summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/perfect-numbers/yunxi/summary-sum-1.mp3",
      "duration": 2.34,
      "size": 37440,
      "text": "完全数等于自己真因数之和，盈数偏多，亏数偏少。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-2",
      "filename": "summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "path": "audio/narrations/perfect-numbers/yunxi/summary-sum-2.mp3",
      "duration": 1.91,
      "size": 30528,
      "text": "亲和数则互为对方真因数之和，成双成对。"
    },
    {
      "script_id": "perfect-numbers",
      "section_id": "summary",
      "line_id": "sum-3",
